metadata.name: Cove 001
metadata.description:
The golden hour. The perfect time to catch the water dancing and glistening in the light- rays of sunshine illuminate this cove off the coast of San Luis Obispo. Dive into the welcoming depths of this magical place and never look back.

Captured on 35mm color film

(Collectors will receive THREE additional pieces of artwork with this purchase; please contact me after buying)
